data.description: Enjoy Diamond Head, city and garden views from this breezy second floor townhouse in Parkview Village! You'll appreciate the convenience of being located minutes from freeway on/off ramps, shopping, restaurants and banks. This townhome features 2 bedrooms with 1.5 bathrooms and TWO parking stalls with ample street parking for your guests. A lanai with panoramic views is perfect for enjoying the breezes without any neighbors in the back! A perfect starter home or investment waiting for your personal touch. Schedule your showing today!
